# 🧠 Brain Tumor Detection using Deep Learning

An AI-powered web application that detects brain tumors from MRI images using a ResNet50-based deep learning model. The system classifies MRI scans into different tumor types and provides prediction confidence through a clean and modern web interface.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧠 Brain tumor classification (Glioma, Meningioma, Pituitary, No Tumor)
- ⚡ Fast prediction using a trained ResNet50 model
- 🌐 Flask-based web application
- 🎨 Modern dark-themed UI with animations
- 📸 Image upload and preview
- 📊 Prediction confidence display

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS (Dark UI, Animations)
- **Backend:** Flask (Python)
- **Model:** ResNet50 (TensorFlow / Keras)
- **Libraries:** NumPy, Pillow

